{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"245","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"購物袋收費有用？ 英調查：海底塑膠袋真的減少了","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>英國獨立報報導，英政府科學家彙整了25年來從海底收集的塑膠垃圾資料，長期追蹤英國周邊海域垃圾量的變化。近期發現海床上的塑膠袋數量明顯減少，顯示打擊塑膠污染的確有所成果。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>雖然從調查結果看來塑膠袋減量政策有用，但專家表示，該報告也指出，還有其他種類的垃圾跟塑膠袋一樣需要被好好處理。因為儘管塑膠購物袋減少，其他塑膠垃圾（特別是塑膠瓶和廢棄漁具）的數量卻在增加，讓海底垃圾的總數大致上保持不變。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0416.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 449px;' /><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'>研究人員從海底清出大批廢棄漁網。圖片來源：NOAA / NMFS / Pacific Islands Fisheries Science Center Blog（CC BY 2.0）</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>這份調查報告發表前不久，另一份政府報告也指出，世界海洋中塑膠的數量將在十年內翻三倍。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>為了解決塑膠禍害，英國政府已經推出各種措施來處理塑膠廢棄物，最近一次是塑膠瓶押金回收計劃。超市購物袋收費已讓全英國塑膠袋使用量下降80％，部會首長們高興地表示這是塑膠廢棄物戰爭的一場勝利。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>主持最新調查報告的「環境、漁業水產養殖科學中心」（Centre for Environment, Fisheries and Aquaculture Science，Cefas）多位科學家也認為，他們觀察到的海底塑膠袋減少的現象，可能跟這個政策有關。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>報告第一作者、Cefas海洋垃圾專家馬耶斯（Thomas Maes）博士說：「看到整個社會，無論是公眾、產業、非政府組織還是政府，減少塑膠袋的努力確實有效果，相當令人振奮。與2010年相比，我們觀察到英國周圍海域拖網撈到塑膠袋的比例明顯下降，顯示只要我們合作，就可以達成減少、重複利用和回收，解決海洋垃圾問題。」</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>馬耶斯和同事分析1992年至2017年間，漁船2461次拖網的捕獲物，發現撈到至少一片塑膠垃圾的比例高達63％。<a href='https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0048969718306442?via%3Dihub#!' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(95, 151, 8); text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'>該研究</a>發表於期刊《全面環境科學》（Science of the Total Environment）。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0416%202.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 450px;' /><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'>海床上發現的塑膠袋。圖片來源：NOAA OKEANOS EXPLORER Program; Our Deepwater Backyard: Exploring Atlantic Canyons and Seamounts 2014（CC BY 2.0）</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>過去的研究發現，海洋生態系統中到處都有塑膠，海底和海溝內都可發現塑膠垃圾。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>學界對塑膠在海洋環境中會造成什麼影響仍然不甚瞭解。不過，許多研究已發現動物會因吃下塑膠或是被塑膠垃圾纏繞而死，塑膠甚至和珊瑚礁疾病有關。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>資料來源:http://e-info.org.tw/node/210940</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-04-16","clk_count":"245"}},"__N_SSG":true}